            <a data-toggle="collapse" class="" href="#faq1">How would I get my products? <i class="icofont-simple-up"></i></a>
            <div id="faq1" class="collapse show" data-parent=".faq-list">
              <p>
                Once the order is processed after successful communication with the tailor, we would initiate the shipping process for the consumer.
              </p>
            </div>
          </li>

          <li data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
            <a data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq2" class="collapsed">What if I'm unsatisfied with the product? <i class="icofont-simple-up"></i></a>
            <div id="faq2" class="collapse" data-parent=".faq-list">
              <p>
                You can contact the creator or you can email us. We would intiate the refund ASAP.
              </p>
            </div>
          </li>

          <li data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="300">
            <a data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq3" class="collapsed">Can I become a tailor on your site?<i class="icofont-simple-up"></i></a>
            <div id="faq3" class="collapse" data-parent=".faq-list">
